<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Generic<sp/>interaction<sp/>between<sp/>two<sp/>entities:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`target`<sp/>–<sp/>Entity<sp/>affected<sp/>by<sp/>the<sp/>interaction</highlight></codeline>
