<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`causer`<sp/>–<sp/>Entity<sp/>that<sp/>directly<sp/>caused<sp/>the<sp/>interaction<sp/>(e.g.<sp/>projectile)</highlight></codeline>
